sequenceDiagram
  participant Developer
  participant CICD as CI/CD Pipeline
  participant Docker
  participant Deployment
  participant CoreSystems as Core Systems (PMS, MMS)
  participant Factories
  participant DB as PostgreSQL/MongoDB

  Developer->>CICD: Commit new update
  CICD->>Docker: Build and package image
  Docker->>Deployment: Push image to registry
  Deployment->>CoreSystems: Deploy updated services
  CoreSystems->>Factories: Send updated control logic
  Deployment->>DB: Log deployment metadata
